in a library in Munich.

135
00:14:14,341 --> 00:14:17,242
It would have been easy
to kill him there.

136
00:14:18,011 --> 00:14:19,877
But I can't kill him.

137
00:14:20,481 --> 00:14:23,542
Dr. Tenma is the one
who's to be left.

138
00:14:24,718 --> 00:14:27,551
He'll be the one left in the end. ..
all alone.

139
00:14:28,288 --> 00:14:30,484
He's going to die
alone and sad.

140
00:14:31,125 --> 00:14:32,559
Without a name.

141
