This is part of Johan's plan.

142
00:14:38,966 --> 00:14:43,369
Dr. Tenma will be allowed to
see the sight Johan has seen.

143
00:14:44,071 --> 00:14:46,267
I want to see that sight, too.

144
00:14:47,374 --> 00:14:48,933
