see those pictures?!

174
00:17:05,779 --> 00:17:06,746
Where did you see them?!

175
00:17:10,517 --> 00:17:12,747
Th-The hill to the south...

176
00:17:14,121 --> 00:17:15,350
At the "Vampire's House."

177
00:17:28,936 --> 00:17:31,132
Hey. Does anybody know?

178
00:17:32,005 --> 00:17:35,236
Do you know where my son is?
Hey...

179
00:17:35,909 --> 00:17:38,003
Wim, where did you go?!

180
00:17:39,746 --> 00:17:42,443
Everyone's dead.

181
00:17:48,488 --> 00:17:49,455
It's the devil.

182
00:17:52,826 --> 00:17:58,265
The devil has come
to this town!

183
00:18:02,769 --> 00:18:05,170
There's no one here
anymore.

184
00:18:12,579 --> 00:18:17,210
Johan was here just
a moment ago doing that.

185
00:18:18,185 --> 00:18:19,152
Is that what you're saying?

186
