They're all attempts at
drawing the two of you.

187
00:18:23,924 --> 00:18:25,392
But they were left unfinished.

188
00:18:27,260 --> 00:18:29,957
All the pictures look like
they're smiling affectionately...

189
00:18:31,765 --> 00:18:34,996
But did Franz Bonaparta
draw these pictures?

190
00:18:35,969 --> 00:18:38,802
What did Johan do upon
seeing these pictures?

191
00:18:39,840 --> 00:18:40,466
...home.

192
