I'm sorry.

206
00:20:05,759 --> 00:20:07,090
Why are you apologizing?

207
00:20:08,762 --> 00:20:09,729
That time...

208
00:20:14,067 --> 00:20:17,503
The two of you
have to keep on living.

209
00:20:19,539 --> 00:20:20,938
The two of you, keep on living.

210
00:20:26,513 --> 00:20:27,503
Why are you crying?

211
00:20:30,050 --> 00:20:31,279
Why are you crying?!

212
00:20:32,919 --> 00:20:33,943
Don't cry!

213
00:20:34,588 --> 00:20:35,555
Don't cry!

