Don't cry!

218
00:20:50,103 --> 00:20:50,695
Nina!

219
00:20:57,978 --> 00:20:58,604
Nina?

220
00:21:01,548 --> 00:21:03,744
He.. .was crying.

221
00:21:05,819 --> 00:21:06,479
Nina...

222
00:21:10,490 --> 00:21:11,423
In this room...

223
00:21:13,059 --> 00:21:16,495
